snippet.title: AMBER HEARD PARODY- Forgetful & confused, AH talks about #metoo experience, L´oreal and Aquaman!
snippet.description:
Hi there!
My name is Carla Yang; Hope you are having a great day; Welcome to my channel!

Today's video is an interview parody about Amber Heard, created for entertainment purposes only.

Video description:
Amber seems a bit confused and forgetful when describing the female experience and empowerment, she also talks about working with Loreal, the slogan "Because you're worth it" and her role as Mera in the film "Aquaman".

I hope you like this video, please let me know in the comment section what you think of it!

Please check out the original interview which I'm sharing down below so you can enjoy the parody even better!

Thanks for staying tuned!, please be safe out there.
See you soon!

Link to original interview:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n0wPLkTUI-o&t=193s

#amberheard #johnnydepp #loreal
